Hangman game using socket communication
============================================================
 This is Embedded SW project
 Project Name : Hangman game using socket communication
 Language : C, Linux
 team member : ku chang mo, HCW
-----------------------------------------------------------
1. step 1
> connection with soket communication

2. step 2
> game start(Game program auto start or user's decision)

3. step 3
> One become an attacker and the other becomes a defender.
> The attacker givers the defender the wrong words and simple tips.

4. step 4
> Defenders use tips to write words.
> Only ten chances.

